  "comment": "BTF440Z Mini Fresnel Zoom 4x 40W RGBW COB LED: The BeamZ BTF440Z is a compact mini LED Fresnel specially designed for short distance coloured wash applications. The fixture is equipped with a tuneable 4x 40W RGBW COB LED. Featuring a 25-80 degree manual zoom function, high quality optics and the use of a compact aluminium housing this mini Fresnel is ideal for theatres, schools, exhibitions and display lighting.\n\n",
